quote.summary: Dingdang Health Technology Group Ltd is an investment holding company principally engaged in the provision of pharmaceutical and healthcare business. The Company is mainly engaged in three businesses. The drug express business mainly sells products through online direct sales, business distribution and offline retail channels, provides express medicine, medical and healthcare services, as well as advertisement, promotion, marketing service and research and development for pharmaceutical products. The online medical consultation business mainly provides users with online consultation services such as medication, nutrition and healthcare services through applied pharmaceutical artificial intelligence (AI) products, Dingdang Pharmacist and Nutritionist AI Assistant. The chronic diseases and health management business mainly provides users with health portfolio management and directly observed therapy (DOT) medication adherence services.
